frame work 框架，指的是一些可以重复使用的样式
响应式框架，指的是可以根据屏幕像素的不同而呈现不同像素大小的框架

一般1024 1200 的使用960pixel，

in css, we use xxx {}  xxx is html label name
				.xxx{} .xxx is class name xxx

padding:10px inside elemnt (padding will compress itself)
margin:10px  outside elemnt(margin will push others ,so will push them out of their place

overflow:auto  combine with height width, you can creat inside slipbar

media query:
	@media only screen and (max-width: 300px)  
	@media: this is a media query:
	only: compatible with old browser
	screen: apply to screen
	and : logical
	max-width:300px:  only apply this rule if max-width is small than 300

think about structure( which column , how many width(colunm)
